original: Fritzell, Karl Johan Erik, bankdirektör, Nässjö, f. 1/4/05 i Ljungby av Johan F. o. Augusta Linder. G. 31 m. Agnes Schölander. Barn: Jan f. 33, Lars 35. — Realex. 21. Anst. i A-B Smålands Bank sed. 21.
translated: Fritzell, Karl Johan Erik, Bank Director, Nässjö, born on 1/4/1905 in Ljungby to Johan F. and Augusta Linder. Married on 31/xx/19xx to Agnes Schölander. Children: Jan born in 1933, Lars born in 1935. Completed Realexamination (a type of secondary school examination) at the age of 21. Employed at A-B Smålands Bank since 1921.
